'''Moji Olaiya''' (27 February 1975 – 17 May 2017) was a Nigerian actress.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pulse.ng/celebrities/moji-olaiya-photos-from-her-40th-birthday-bash-id3535584.html|title=Moji Olaiya: Photos from her 40th birthday bash|website=The Pulse|author=Esho Wemimo|accessdate=26 March 2015}}</ref>
